{"id":302832,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-举牌天安门连闯美使馆，女冤民王尾珠求/","date":"2013-07-09T02:33:37Z","modified":"2013-07-09T02:33:37Z","title":"维权网 | 举牌天安门连闯美使馆，女冤民王尾珠求坐牢（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\">（维权网信息员令新报道）昨天（7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>日）下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>4</span></span><span>点，走投无路的福建三明女冤民王尾珠只身再次勇闯北京美使馆抛洒传单（诉告材料）告洋状，被北京朝阳分局麦子店派出所抓走时，走投无路的她竟令人匪夷所思地向警察主动强烈要求二进宫再坐牢。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span>原来王尾珠因儿子被他人杀害，当地警方在犯罪嫌疑人的年龄上公开作假，导致重罪轻判。王尾珠强烈不服，长期上访控告无果，反遭毫无人性的当地徇私枉法公安的非法拘留等各种迫害，绝望的王尾珠曾在北京上访时喝农药自杀。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span></span></p>\n<div><span>去年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>11</span></span><span>日诉告无门的王尾珠，被逼进京寻求著名艺术家艾未未先生帮助维权，没想到同样被抓回福州拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>天后，再无端被劳教</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1</span></span><span>年！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span></span><span></span><br /><span>今年七一党庆日，刚刚解教释放才几天的王尾珠，就和另</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>11</span></span><span>福州冤民一起集体闯美使馆告洋状，又被拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>5</span></span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span></span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>日走投无路的王尾珠又独自到北京天安门前举牌喊冤，被天安门分局警察抓走关到马家楼黑监狱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<div><span>据了解王尾珠的福州冤民石立琴介绍，王尾珠不堪屡遭当地徇私枉法警方报复迫害，已被逼上梁山，在没了活路下只得举牌天安门、勇闯美使馆诉冤求坐牢，反正被抓回当地也是要把她再送进监狱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<div><span>可见诉告无门的女冤民王尾珠，比永州唐慧的命运更为悲惨百倍！敬请各界高度关注现再次被抓进北京朝阳分局麦子店派出所正待处理的王尾珠！！！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span><span>王尾珠电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>13215900397</span></span></div>\n<p><span></span><span>石立琴电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>18950274974</span></span><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-D3NlNdyQyjY/UdtmJZFfGYI/AAAAAAAAlBg/61abvBQHBFo/s1600/%E7%8E%8B%E5%B0%BE%E7%8F%A01_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-D3NlNdyQyjY/UdtmJZFfGYI/AAAAAAAAlBg/61abvBQHBFo/s400/%E7%8E%8B%E5%B0%BE%E7%8F%A01_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-BZhFlK9ZLZc/UdtmF0m_IPI/AAAAAAAAlBQ/GMiZBxg2d24/s1600/%E7%8E%8B%E5%B0%BE%E7%8F%A05.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-BZhFlK9ZLZc/UdtmF0m_IPI/AAAAAAAAlBQ/GMiZBxg2d24/s400/%E7%8E%8B%E5%B0%BE%E7%8F%A05.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-oZXXkrtvpgs/UdtmF1jqHwI/AAAAAAAAlBU/73MA6CP5roY/s1600/%E7%8E%8B%E5%B0%BE%E7%8F%A07.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-oZXXkrtvpgs/UdtmF1jqHwI/AAAAAAAAlBU/73MA6CP5roY/s400/%E7%8E%8B%E5%B0%BE%E7%8F%A07.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span><br /><span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div> </div>\n<div> </div>\n<div><span></span> </div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"ta